### ==== SPECIALIZATION CRUD OPERATIONS (Dashboard) ====

### Get All Specializations
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/specializations
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### Get Specialization by ID
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/specializations/{{SPECIALIZATION_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### Create New Specialization
POST {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/specializations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "nameAr": "علوم الحاسوب",
  "nameEn": "Computer Science"
}

### Update Specialization
PUT {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/specializations/{{SPECIALIZATION_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "nameAr": "هندسة البرمجيات",
  "nameEn": "Software Engineering"
}

### Delete Specialization
DELETE {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/specializations/{{SPECIALIZATION_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### ==== TEACHERS API WITH FILTERS & PAGINATION ====

### Get All Teachers (Basic - First Page)
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/teachers

### Get All Teachers with Pagination
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/teachers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5

### Get Teachers Filtered by Skills
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/teachers?skillIds={{SKILL_ID_1}}&skillIds={{SKILL_ID_2}}&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Get Teachers with Custom Pagination and No Rating Order
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/teachers?pageNumber=2&pageSize=15&orderByRating=false

### Get Teachers with All Parameters
GET {{Academix.WebAPI_HostAddress}}/api/teachers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20&skillIds={{SKILL_ID_1}}&skillIds={{SKILL_ID_2}}&orderByRating=true

